Class Range

  • java.lang.Object
    • Functions.Range
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Range

    public class Range
extends java.lang.Object
implements Range
    This class can be used to define parts of sheets. One purpose for this is the so called user defined range, which makes it posible for users to refer to ranges with a name in stead of via cell references.
    Author:
    Maarten Flikkema
